{"tid":1157881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被郭台銘酸「只會說發大財」 韓國瑜：高雄會繼續用「念力」提振士氣、提醒市民生活所追求的目標","createTime":"2019-05-16T14:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T02:19:05.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8f38002cac7215087c00ee98fcf341dc43d32b02","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"影／被郭董酸「只會發大財」 韓國瑜：用念力提升士氣<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-16 <br />\n<br />\n鴻海董事長郭台銘今走訪台東，暗酸高雄市長韓國瑜只會說「發大財」，根本不懂庶民經濟。對此，<span style=\"color: red;\">韓國瑜晚間出席擴大反毒宣導座談會後，強調他尊重，但高雄會繼續用「念力」提振士氣、提醒市民生活所追求的目標。</span><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜表示，全高雄都知道「高雄發大財」，幾乎人人都琅琅上口，每次喊這5個字，也都讓高雄市民特別開心；甚至過年發放的「發大財」紅包也全數被海內外民眾搶領，相信對高雄市民而言，「高雄發大財」是一件開心的事，「尊重郭董看法，但我們也有自己的看法」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，立法院前院長王金平日前發表文章時，也曾提到「不能只有發大財」；韓國瑜被問及是否感覺被黨內同志砲口瞄準，他再提「尊重」。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜表示，王金平院長是目前國內輩分最高的政治人物之一，相信他有他的高度、胸襟、氣度、看法，「不論他闡述什麼，我都尊重」。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜表示，自己離開政壇17年，當中心境變化、前半生甚至後半生養成過程，自己心裡都相當清楚。韓國瑜再向郭台銘喊話，「請郭董事長繼續往前衝」，自己也將繼續在工作崗位上做好工作，大家各自努力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3817437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3817437&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=93c6bc4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3817437</a>"},{"pid":"4fbf1440cb515c632487a6936a02d0da2a12f5d6","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58081e58723069f2b3993ad6fbea1579a9218d86","tid":1157881,"uid":810,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmcZyTG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmcZyTG.png&h=28b9ea13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d98a55bcc6fc40a7c78424853dcef3927af43910","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"高雄有89萬人齊齊發功"},{"pid":"f73f6880f54df8791a9ef505d931b13fc05563bf","tid":1157881,"uid":42804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"念力打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5613cbb2d772e7ce407efdd618eb98c168f5eeb7","tid":1157881,"uid":69038,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHdaFzx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHdaFzx.png&h=463b7eed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"363d5fee2d2abf4a397718dc5078453b82b0ce31","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"全台民調最高的候選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國民黨黨內民調最高的候選人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923c3d3f3c20ced1fe0ebef6f82f6f456307a866","tid":1157881,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"363d5fee2d2abf4a397718dc5078453b82b0ce31","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"全台民調最高的候選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國民黨黨內民調最高的候選人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"而家韓國愚民調應該唔係最高，起碼高雄唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中夭、CCTVBS唔敢報民調"},{"pid":"2598d0e797c53d4e8e0e5de2f8c5797bae7b20fa","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"「高雄發大財」答詢傻呼呼？韓國瑜：其實有「神聖目標」<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-16<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜自嘲，他每天講高雄發大財，好像看起來傻呼呼的。（記者洪定宏攝）<br />\n<br />\n〔記者洪定宏／高雄報導〕高雄市長韓國瑜在議會接受議員總質詢時，多次以「高雄發大財」答詢，挨批不用心；今天他受訪時自嘲，每天講高雄發大財，好像看起來傻呼呼的，但實際上有神聖目標與宗旨。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜強調，如果高雄發大財，市民愈來愈好，經濟達到更高層次，就能重視教育並關心弱勢。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;<br />\n<br />\n勁過&quot;國師&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15df46861124d5884aa6d366ff8a36afa644a585","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f78904f76c44b1e49806b3dbe6628a33c56780f","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://boba.ettoday.net/video/231/284/156515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fboba.ettoday.net%2Fvideo%2F231%2F284%2F156515&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=9c280858\" target=\"_blank\">https://boba.ettoday.net/video/231/284/156515</a>"},{"pid":"4c464681d4fa7e8ad2257de95a6990ed98c83b3d","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"念力國防"},{"pid":"c0034f9be8fc4531da230eecd6785034bc343860","tid":1157881,"uid":59632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDC3gFm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDC3gFm.jpg&h=d1ebecc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c431b73ef1da76c6058e8c3854e94d4c4677c6dd","tid":1157881,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T22:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2d6d384622b865de6c8be10f9209128ed0e80a","tid":1157881,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:03:37.000Z","msg":"佢真係傻既"},{"pid":"6e8c7739ffbca4c478d78b636dcb1389119b97d2","tid":1157881,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:41:41.000Z","msg":"柯P出來偷雞啦宜家咁亂"},{"pid":"44215cb15b5ecf1f3e1058eb1392ae19ce1bd0fe","tid":1157881,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"智將救台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a549c709c1a5fe4dc2b37e6a789df307f70ffcd5","tid":1157881,"uid":34409,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVPQJXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVPQJXQ.jpg&h=cdb7c847&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57aef8233c0a2b27a16c66fb695edbdadf98cd97","tid":1157881,"uid":149008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:06:51.000Z","msg":"請尊重，謝謝！"},{"pid":"cb535985e37282e12bf5cd27966ba6cad414e09b","tid":1157881,"uid":62850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:07:42.000Z","msg":"比卡超：比卡比卡~<br />\n奇異種子：種子種子~<br />\n車厘龜：車厘車厘~<br />\n<br />\n泡菜瑜：發大財發大財~"},{"pid":"4224f35f0d4c284041b56035ff3d5bc664698d4f","tid":1157881,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5702/23490011506_54dc9de2b8_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm6.staticflickr.com%2F5702%2F23490011506_54dc9de2b8_o.jpg&h=10dfe0ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75037eb9967baf04d08f2238edb9f661adfe4fc5","tid":1157881,"uid":143078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:14:57.000Z","msg":"「念力」原來係真㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以攞諾貝爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4329fb927870f11b14e60569288a2b368e78ba43","tid":1157881,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d63a4a1b041633bcb6b02cfc38f2897e55f